{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016wvtxskaa4ygrM8Xt9AqD4","type":"tool_result","content":"   219→- [ ] [on-chain] `join_round` instruction — new player joins an existing round. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active (countdown), player not already in round, player count < 20. Adds PlayerEntry to Vec, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. If this is the 2nd unique player, transition phase Waiting→Active and set `countdown_ends_at = clock + 60`. Verify: bankrun tests for happy path (join triggers countdown), duplicate player rejection, max players rejection, wrong phase rejection.\n   220→- [ ] [on-chain] `buy_more_entries` instruction — existing player buys additional entries. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active, player already in round. Increments player's entry count, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. Verify: bankrun test buys more, checks updated entry count + pool."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eb09418b-9a05-47a7-9018-08de1043e41d","uuid":"9cf28c70-6488-479d-b672-55ab2487121d","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/101-lord-of-the-rngs/spec.md","content":"- [ ] [on-chain] `join_round` instruction — new player joins an existing round. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active (countdown), player not already in round, player count < 20. Adds PlayerEntry to Vec, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. If this is the 2nd unique player, transition phase Waiting→Active and set `countdown_ends_at = clock + 60`. Verify: bankrun tests for happy path (join triggers countdown), duplicate player rejection, max players rejection, wrong phase rejection.\n- [ ] [on-chain] `buy_more_entries` instruction — existing player buys additional entries. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active, player already in round. Increments player's entry count, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. Verify: bankrun test buys more, checks updated entry count + pool.","numLines"